DESCRIPTION
===========

* this amarino plugin will allow to controll the sumorobot via bluetooth over a android phone
* it reacts to loudness around the phone and motion of the phone


INSTALLATION
============

Steps:
1) download Android SDK
2) add it to PATH
3) init the project with Android and download Amarino library
4) install Amarino library for Arduino
5) install Amarino on the phone
6) compile the Amarino plugin
7) install the plugin for Amarino
8) install Arduino program

Commands:
make download_64 or make download_32
make init_64 or make init_32
make init_project
sudo make init_arduino
make install amarino
make all
make install
arduino Moodrobot.ino

Notes:
Enable USB debugging on the Android device

